high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table in the corner.
Turn around and veer right to the multicolored chair.
Place the cell phone on the chair, near the front left corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a cell phone on a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and stand to face the right side of the desk.
Pick the phone up from the desk.
Turn around and face the chair with flowers on it that is behind.
Put the phone on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a phone on a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and take a step forward, turn left and walk over to the wooden desk.
Pick up the phone off of the wooden desk.
Walk over to the flower chair behind you.
Put the phone on the front edge of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move a phone to a chair.
